Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君(しょうぶんくん)）\Nなぜ 昌平君(しょうへいくん)の招集に応じた？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:06.28,Kingdom-Main,Changwenjun,0,0,0,,Why did you respond to Changpingjun's invitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.46,0:00:08.19,Kingdom-Flashback,Pang,0,0,0,,{Flashback Ends}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.87,0:00:11.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君）あれほど秦国(しんこく)軍を\N率いることを拒んでいたお前が―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:11.65,Kingdom-Main,Changwenjun,0,0,0,,You were so fervently against leading the Qin Army before,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:13.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういう風の吹き回しだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:13.46,Kingdom-Main,Changwenjun,0,0,0,,what brought on this change of heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.98,0:00:16.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎(おうき)）意外でしたか？\N（昌文君）当たり前だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:15.47,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Were you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:16.79,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:21.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして戦う気になった？ 王騎\N（王騎）馬陽(ばよう)ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.79,0:00:19.63,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,What caused you to want to fight, Wang Qi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.63,0:00:21.16,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,It's Mayang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.82,0:00:28.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか… そうだったな　馬陽は…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.88,0:00:26.19,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:27.69,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,So that was why...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:28.62,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,Mayang was...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:33.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かつて 六将の摎(きょう)とお前\Nそして わしの３人で―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.77,0:00:32.43,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,the place where you, Great General Liao, and I
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:35.21,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,took a castle from Zhao.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.73,0:00:36.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,趙(ちょう)より奪った城 そして…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.74,0:00:36.72,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.74,0:00:39.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,摎が倒れた地だった…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:39.91,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,the place where Liao was defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:45.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは悪夢だった\Nまさか あの摎が敗れるとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.07,0:00:43.02,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,That was a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:45.00,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,To think that Liao could ever be beaten...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:51.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,龐煖(ほうけん)… 何者だったのか あの男は…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.99,0:00:48.14,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,Pang Nuan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.46,0:00:51.16,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,Who was that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.46,0:00:55.75,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:57.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや よそう　死んだ男の話など
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.75,0:00:57.56,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,We don't need to talk about a dead man...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.45,0:01:02.34,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,But are you saying that you refuse to hand over Mayang as it is the place Liao died?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.49,0:01:02.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では 摎の弔いの地 馬陽は\N渡せぬということか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:05.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎）まあ そんなところです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.14,0:01:05.02,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Well, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.13,0:01:12.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,昌文君 私は そろそろ\N昭王(しょうおう)六将としての自分とは―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:09.01,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Changwenjun, I've been thinking I should perhaps soon bid farewell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.53,0:01:14.84,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,to my self that was one of the Six Great Generals under King Zhao.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:14.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決別しようかと考えています
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:20.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この戦いを決着として\N（昌文君）決着？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.89,0:01:19.47,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,In order to settle this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:20.56,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,Settle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.15,0:01:25.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ようやく\Nお前も前へ進む気になったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:25.23,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,So you've finally decided to move forward, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:30.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎）そうできればと\N自分に期待しているところです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.99,0:01:30.23,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,If I can. It's an expectation I have for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.86,0:02:12.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）始皇(しこう)３年３月\N秦国軍総大将の王騎が出陣した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:08.96,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Shi Huang Year 3, Month 3,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:12.42,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Supreme Commander of the State of Qin Army, Wang Qi departed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:16.18,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, the soldiers heading to Mayang...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:16.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのころ\N馬陽に向かう歩兵たちは…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:18.49,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We'll now form Wu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:20.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（千人将）\Nこれより伍(ご)を作る！ 伍長 集まれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:20.04,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Wuchang, gather!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:23.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平(びへい)）やべえ！\N伍作りが始まっちまったぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:22.56,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Aw, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:23.98,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,They've already started forming Wu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:26.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾到(びとう)）信(しん)が まだ来てねえのに！\N（尾平）あのバカ野郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.98,0:02:25.45,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,But Xin isn't even here yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:26.91,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,That goddamn idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:34.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（馬のいななき）\N（信）ドウ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:34.04,Kingdom-Main,Gin,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:36.17,Kingdom-Main,Gin,0,0,0,,Is everybody here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:36.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな そろってっか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:43.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）\N時は紀元前 春秋戦国時代の秦国
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.32,0:02:40.66,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The setting is before the common era,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:42.92,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,in the State of Qin during the Spring and Autumn Warring States Period.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:46.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,名もなき少年 信は\N若き王 政(せい)と出会い―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:47.15,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The nameless boy Xin met with the young King Zheng,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:51.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,武功を挙げて\Nついに 百人隊の将にまでなった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.15,0:02:51.22,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,distinguished himself in war, and finally became a Hundred-Man General.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:57.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな中 突然 隣国の趙が攻め入り\N未曽有の危機が訪れる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.97,0:02:55.49,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Among those events, the neighboring State of Zhao suddenly invaded,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:57.23,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,presenting an unprecedented crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.91,0:03:01.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,総大将 王騎は\Nいかなる戦いを仕掛けるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:03:01.93,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,What kind of war will Supreme Commander Wang Qi wage?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.85,0:03:05.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして\N信は いかなる成長を遂げるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:05.65,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,And what kind of growth with Xin achieve?
