Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:46.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂(てん)）でも 大丈夫なのか？\N勝手に戦場を見に行ったりして
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:46.26,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,But are you sure about this? Going on our own to see the battlefield?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:49.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙毅(もうき)）大丈夫\N先生の許可は もらったから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:47.72,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:50.13,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,I got Teacher's permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:52.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,秦国軍総司令のお墨付きだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:52.72,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,That's the authorization of the State of Qin Commander-in-Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:55.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂）えっ？ 秦国軍総司令？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:55.74,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,State of Qin Commander-in-Chief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:58.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ま… まさか 蒙毅の先生って…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.01,0:04:58.77,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,A-Are you saying that your teacher is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:03.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう\N呂不韋丞相(りょふいじょうしょう)四柱のひとり 昌平君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:02.68,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,Yes. One of Chancellor Lü Buwei's Four Pillars,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:03.73,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,Changpingjun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:08.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃ… じゃ 政の敵側の…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:08.26,Kingdom-Thought,Diao,0,0,0,,Th-Then, he's on the side of Zheng's enemies... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:10.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心配しないで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:10.09,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:14.33,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,The relationship between the king and the chancellor is totally unrelated to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:14.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大王と丞相とのことは\N僕には関係ないから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:18.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は ただ戦場を見て\Nその風に触れていたいだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:18.52,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,I just want to see a battlefield and feel the wind there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:26.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂）な… なあ 蒙毅\N勝つよな？ この戦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:24.56,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Meng Yi,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:27.05,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,We'll win, right? This war?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:31.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦は\N始まってみなければ分からないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:30.80,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,We won't know unless we actually see the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:34.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも そうあってほしいと思ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:34.40,Kingdom-Main,Yi,0,0,0,,But... I do hope we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:37.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂）信…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:37.54,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Xin...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:48.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初に言っておく！\Nこの隊は ただの百人隊じゃねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:49.10,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I'll say this first! This unit is no ordinary Hundred-Man Unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:50.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,特殊百人部隊だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:50.67,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,It's a Special Hundred-Man Unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:53.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）と… 特殊百人部隊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:53.06,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,S-Special Hundred-Man Unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:55.00,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:56.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）\Nそうだ！ どの大隊にも所属せず
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.75,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,We're not attached to any large battalion,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:06:01.22,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I heard from General Wang Qi himself that we're a special unit working directly under him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:59.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王騎将軍直属の\N特殊部隊になることを―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:01.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,将軍本人から聞いてきた！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:08.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かといって\N特殊部隊ってのが何なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:07.72,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Having said that, what exactly is a Special Unit, you may ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:11.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何をする隊なのかは\N俺にも分からねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:11.10,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What our unit will be doing, even I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.54,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,But I can say this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが これだけは言える！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.44,0:06:16.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,将軍が この隊を\Nほかと色分けしたってことは―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:16.74,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,The fact that the general has classified this unit differently from the others
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:19.58,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,means that we will see a more important battlefield than the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:19.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかよりも\N重要な戦地に充てるってことだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:21.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひょっとしたら―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:23.94,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,We may be sent to assault someplace really huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とんでもねえとこに\N突撃させられるかもしれねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:26.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？ ヒイッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:27.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）だが その分…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:27.64,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,But in return...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:33.33,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,the distinguishment we'll receive will undoubtedly be gigantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.89,0:06:33.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,挙げる武功は\N間違いなくバカでけえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:40.40,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,The majority of this unit is made up of the stalwarts that survived the Shegan Plain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:37.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）この部隊の大半が―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:40.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの蛇甘(だかん)平原で\N生き残った猛者たちだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:44.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちが力を束ねれば\Nどんな敵にも立ち向かえる！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:44.19,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,If we combine our strengths, we can stand against any enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:46.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいか？ てめえら！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:46.35,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Got that, guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:49.97,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,We'll crush that Zhao Army that carelessly strolled in here in an attempt to attack us
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:49.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ノコノコ攻めてきやがった趙軍を\Nたたきつぶし…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:52.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魏(ぎ)との戦いよりも…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.23,0:06:53.01,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,and get our hands
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:58.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,更に でっけえ武功を―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.69,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,on even greater glory
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:07:00.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つかみ取るぞー！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:07:01.02,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,than in the war with Wei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:08.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（渕(えん)）さすが 信どの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:08.62,Kingdom-Thought,Yuan,0,0,0,,Lord Xin really is something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:11.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初の檄(げき)で\N一気に隊の心をつかんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:11.74,Kingdom-Thought,Yuan,0,0,0,,In his first speech, he immediately captured everyone's hearts! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:14.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（農兵Ａ）\Nすげえ… あいつ ホントに信か？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:14.40,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Awesome! Is that guy really Xin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:16.17,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:16.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（農兵Ｂ）\Nどうなってんだ？ こりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:18.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信 お前…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:18.40,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Xin... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:21.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（農兵Ｃ）あのガキ\Nこの半年で何かあったッスね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:22.09,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,That kid, something must've happened to him in these past six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:23.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（沛浪(はいろう)）ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:22.76,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:25.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それから この隊には―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:27.96,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Moving on, I've been allowed to assign two vice generals to this unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:28.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人の副将を置くことを\N許してもらった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:29.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人目は渕さんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:29.80,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,The first is Mr. Yuan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（渕）よろしく！\N（兵士たち）はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:31.88,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Greetings!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:36.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう１人の副将は？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:35.89,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,And the other vice general?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:42.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）\Nああ まだ来てねえみてえだがな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.71,0:07:42.68,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Yeah... It looks like he's not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:48.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）心配すんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:48.42,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:52.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし あいつが来なくても\Nこの部隊は強(つえ)え！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:51.88,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Even if he doesn't come, this unit is strong!
