Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.14,0:07:54.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ナレーター）\N王騎軍にとって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:54.69,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,For General Wang Qi,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:58.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,咸陽(かんよう)から馬陽までは\N15日の道のりである
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.69,0:07:57.76,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,the journey from Xiangyang to Mayang would take 15 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:00.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一方 信たち歩兵軍は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:03.86,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Xin and his group marched from a location that would take 9 more days to reach Mayang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:04.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと９日の所まで行軍を進めていた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:04.08,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,0)\bord4\fs30\3c&HA8A7A8&\pos(210.667,563.001)}Xiangyang {Bottom. Just do static signs until the camera zooms out.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:04.08,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,0)\bord4\fs30\3c&HAD478B&\pos(622.667,397.666)}Wang Qi \NArmy {Purple}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:04.08,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,0)\bord4\fs30\3c&HB08058&\pos(702.666,327.001)}Foot Soldiers {Blue}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:04.08,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,0)\bord4\fs30\3c&HA8A7A8&\pos(982.66,280.334)}Mayang {Right}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:17.31,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Ow! What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:17.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:27.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なに夜中に\Nひとりでニヤけてんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:26.94,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,What're you grinning about alone in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.18,0:08:31.38,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Hey, I wasn't grinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:31.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,べ… 別に ニヤけてねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:34.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハハッ… とぼけるなって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:34.73,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:37.89,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,I knew you'd be excited about being a Hundred-Man General.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:40.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがに うれしいよな 百人将は\N（信）当ったり前(めえ)だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:40.61,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:44.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,100人を率いる隊長だもんな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:43.76,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Being a captain that leads a hundred people...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:48.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１年前まで里典(りてん)の下僕で\N村いちばんのバカと言われたお前が
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:48.82,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,And to think, a year ago, you were Li Dian's servant and were called the stupidest guy in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:51.13,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,But now you're leading the guys from that village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:53.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その村の連中を率いるってんだから\N本当に すごいことだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.49,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,This really is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:56.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“バカ”は余計だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:55.95,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You didn't need that "stupid" part!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:59.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと 村いちばんは尾平だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:59.10,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What's more, Wei Ping was the stupidest in the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.07,0:09:04.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど 俺らも うれしいんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:03.86,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,But, I'm happy for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:11.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃそうさ　あんな田舎村の\Nしょうもねえ俺たちの中から―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.50,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:11.63,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Somebody from our wretched lot in that country village
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:13.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,百人将が出たんだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:13.65,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,actually became a Hundred-Man General.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:17.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兄貴なんて\N隣村の連中にも威張りまくりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:16.85,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Even Big Brother was boasting like crazy to the guys in the neighboring village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:19.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,子分が百人将になったってな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.17,0:09:19.52,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,"One of my followers became a Hundred-Man General".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:23.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フン… なにが子分だ あの野郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:22.92,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,That bastard. Who the hell's a follower?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:26.32,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,You've finally taken your first step to being a great general.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:26.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いよいよ 将としての第１歩だな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:29.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,張り切り過ぎて\Nムチャだけは勘弁しろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:28.77,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,Just don't get so full you yourself, sometimes you go too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:31.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 任せとけ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:30.84,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:35.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）\Nしかし 馬陽に近づくにつれ―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:35.51,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,But as they got closer to Mayang,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:39.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,歩兵たちの中には\N趙軍の情報が流れ始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:39.18,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,information about the Zhao Army started to spread through the group of the foot soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:46.66,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Did you hear? About the Zhao Army?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:47.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士Ａ）聞いたか？ 趙軍のこと\N（兵士Ｂ）ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.66,0:09:50.69,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Yeah. I heard they gathered together the people from a castle they took and killed them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:50.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落とした城の人間集めて\N皆殺しにしたらしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:53.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士Ｃ）\N老人 女から赤子に至るまで―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:56.20,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,I heard they killed every last person, down to the elderly, the women, and the infants!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:56.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人残らず殺されたんだとよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:59.46,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,They went that far...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:59.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士Ｄ）\Nそこまでやるのか 趙軍は…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:06.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士Ａ）なあ 俺たち\Nそいつらと殺し合いするのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:05.73,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Hey, are we gonna be fighting those guys to the death?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:13.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マズイ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:15.68,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,This is bad! Lord Xin, their morale is dropping!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:17.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信どの 士気が下がっている\Nこれでは とても戦など…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:17.28,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,In this state, they can't win any sort of battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:24.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チッ… 何ビビってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:24.61,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What're they scared of?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:30.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいか？ お前ら\N趙のヤツらは もう目の前だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:28.03,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Listen up, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.03,0:10:30.36,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,We're about to face those Zhao guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:33.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちで趙軍を蹴散らし―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:33.13,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,We're going to scatter the Zhao Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:35.06,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,and when they're surrounded and waiting for reinforcements,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:37.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,包囲されて助けを待ってる馬陽を\N解放してやるんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:36.91,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,we'll release Mayang from their control!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.37,0:10:38.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かったか！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:38.51,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:43.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつら…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:43.08,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,These guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:50.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん？ 何だ？ この音は
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.50,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,What is this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.72,0:10:54.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お… おい… 後ろ見ろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:53.33,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:54.49,Kingdom-Main,Dao,0,0,0,,L-Look behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.39,0:10:56.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）何だ？\N（兵士）どうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:56.44,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What is it? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:22.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ンッフ～ン…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:11:59.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎）ンフッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:02.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全軍…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:02.59,Kingdom-Main,Wang Qi,0,0,0,,All units...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:11.30,Kingdom-Main,Wang Qi,0,0,0,,forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前進！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:31.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,す… すげえ…\Nたったひと言で これかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:30.22,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,A-Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.02,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,He did this with one sentence?! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:34.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがだぜ 王騎将軍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:34.23,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,General Wang Qi really is great! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:42.60,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,With the Wang Qi's at the front, the State of Qin Army's spirits are raised...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:42.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ンフッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:47.50,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,but that night, disquieting information was leaked to the capital, Xiangyang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:47.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）\N王騎の出陣で 意気上がる秦国軍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:53.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが その夜 王都 咸陽には\N不穏な情報がもたらされた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:53.25,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,{Eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:58.69,Kingdom-Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(800,800)\fs40\pos(649.334,509)}State of Qin     {\fs50}Xiangyang
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:57.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大臣）報告！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:58.10,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:13:00.34,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We've finally learned who the Supreme Commander of the Zhao Army is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.16,0:13:00.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ようやく趙軍の総大将が\N分かりました！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:04.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（呂不韋）うん？ 誰じゃ？ 申せ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:04.26,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,Who is it? Speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.46,0:13:07.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大臣）はっ！ 龐煖という者です\N（李斯(りし)）龐煖？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:06.39,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! Someone called Pang Nuan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:07.73,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,Pang Nuan...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:10.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌平君）\N聞いたことがない　何者だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:10.47,Kingdom-Main,Changpingjun,0,0,0,,I've never heard of him. Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:20.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした？ 昌文君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:20.90,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Changwenjun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:23.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほ… 龐煖だと？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:23.30,Kingdom-Main,Changwenjun,0,0,0,,P-Pang Nuan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:26.11,Kingdom-Main,Changwenjun,0,0,0,,Impossible... It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:27.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな… ありえぬ\Nヤツは死んだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:27.70,Kingdom-Main,Changwenjun,0,0,0,,He's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.21,0:13:30.82,Kingdom-Main,Changwenjun,0,0,0,,He was killed nine years ago by Wang Qi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:30.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,９年前 王騎に殺されたはず
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:40.67,Kingdom-Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(800,0)\fs30\pos(813.334,511.667)}Zhao Army\N Supreme Commander
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:40.67,Kingdom-Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(800,0)\fs50\pos(1028,506.334)}Pang Nuan
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:40.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（龐煖）王騎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:40.06,Kingdom-Main,Pang,0,0,0,,Wang Qi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:11.58,Kingdom-Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(644,659.667)}Qiang Lei
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:20.80,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You finish what you had to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:21.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）用事は済んだのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.28,0:14:24.16,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,No. My enemy moved from Wei to Zhao.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:24.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羌瘣(きょうかい)）\Nいや 敵は魏から趙へ移っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:28.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）んじゃ\Nまた趙へ行くために参戦だな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:28.33,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,So you joined the war again in order to go to Zhao, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:31.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羌瘣）そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:30.90,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:36.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）\Nよし！ これで俺の百人隊 完成だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:36.24,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Okay! Now my Hundred-Man Unit is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:40.26,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Glad to have you with us, Qiang Lei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:40.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よろしく頼むぜ 羌瘣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:43.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,緑穂(りょくすい)が…\N（信）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:42.54,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Lu Sui...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:46.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羌瘣）緑穂がいらだっている
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:46.67,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Lu Sui is getting impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:50.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羌瘣）過酷な戦いになるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.41,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,This is going to be a brutal battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:53.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘヘッ… 望むところだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:53.74,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You'll get just what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.01,0:14:56.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それよか 剣を抜いたついでに\Nあれ見せてくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:57.20,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Well, now that you've got your sword drawn, why don't you show me that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:15:00.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのトントンタ～ンとかいう あれ\N俺も覚えてえし
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:15:00.32,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I wanna learn that "tontontaan" thingy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:04.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ… 相変わらず大バカだな お前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:04.17,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,You're as huge a fool as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.74,0:15:06.14,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:06.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なにぃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:19.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羌瘣）蚩尤(しゆう)は\N荒ぶる神を鎮める巫女(みこ)の力を―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:20.93,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,The Chi You... turns the power of maiden mediums that appeases malevolent gods into fighting techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:21.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦いの技に変えた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:25.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,陶酔の中で舞って\N周囲の敵を切り裂いていく
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.66,0:15:25.74,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,We dance in an ecstasy and cut apart the enemies around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:29.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自らに神を堕(お)とす奥義だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:28.80,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,They are secret techniques that makes gods descend at our will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:32.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰にもマネできるものではない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:32.61,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,They are not something that others can imitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:36.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,か… 神？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.05,0:15:36.40,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,G-Gods?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:40.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんか よく分かんねえけど\Nお前らだけ ズルくねえか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:40.82,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I don't really get it, but isn't it a little unfair only you guys can use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:42.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神さん味方にしてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:42.64,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Making gods your allies and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:47.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蚩尤だけではない\Nそれに もっと恐ろしい者がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:44.96,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,It's not just the Chi You.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:47.61,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Also... there are more fearsome ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:51.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,荒ぶる神を堕とすのではなく\Nもともと体に宿す者だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:49.74,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Ones that do not simply bring down the malevolent gods,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:51.54,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,they dwell within their bodies from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:55.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,体に… 宿す？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:55.26,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Within... their bodies?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:58.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを我々は“武神”と呼ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:58.61,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,They are the ones we call the War Gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:15:59.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,武神…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:15:59.83,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,War Gods?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:04.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（李斯）\N龐煖が 六大将軍 摎を討っただと？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:04.77,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,Pang Nuan killed Liao of the Six Great Generals?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:09.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（呂不韋）六将 摎は\N病にふして逝(い)ったと聞いていたが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:09.30,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,I had heard that Great General Liao perished by succumbing to illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:11.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違ったのか？ 昌文君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:11.17,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,is that incorrect, Changwenjun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:21.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,病死というのは\N王騎とわしで画策した作り話だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:21.02,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,The illness was a story Wang Qi and I created.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.69,0:16:25.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,摎は龐煖に殺された　それが真実だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:23.64,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,Liao was killed by Pang Nuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:25.94,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,That is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:32.62,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,So he is quite a military commander,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:34.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（呂不韋）いかなる武将なのだ？\Nその龐煖なる者は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:34.60,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,that one called Pang Nuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:37.02,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,He is not a military commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:39.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君）武将ではない\N（呂不韋）なに？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:38.85,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:43.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの男のことは\Nほとんど分からぬが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.61,0:16:44.84,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,I know very little about that man, but this much I can say for certain...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:45.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これだけは言える
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:50.53,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,He is, by no means, the sort of person to lead people like a military general!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:49.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは 武将のように\N人を率いるたぐいの者ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:50.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決して
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.37,0:16:53.65,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,That man is a complete army himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.39,0:16:53.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの男は完全なる“個”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:59.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや あれは もっと…\Nおぞましいほどに純粋な…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:56.23,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,No, he is more...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:17:01.95,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,To a repulsive degree, he is a pure manifestation of "war" itself...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:01.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,武の結晶だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:09.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君）９年前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:08.72,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,Nine years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:14.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの男は秦国軍10万の ど真ん中に\N１人で現れた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:12.55,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,that man appeared in the middle of a Qin Army of 100,000 soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:13.93,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,completely alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:18.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（見張り）おい 止まれ！\Nここは大将軍の宿営だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.32,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey, stop! {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:18.35,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,This is a Great General's camp! {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:21.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこで止まり 所属を答えよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:20.93,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Stop right there and state what group you're attached to! {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:23.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全員 構え！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:23.66,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Everyone, take your positions! {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:29.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（斬る音）\N（兵士たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:36.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:43.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では その男―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:43.67,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,So you're saying that on his own
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:47.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たったひとりで総大将を守る布陣を\N突破したというのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:47.62,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,that man broke through the formation protecting the Supreme Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:51.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌平君）あってはならんことだ\N軍を１人で打ち破るなど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:49.55,Kingdom-Main,Changping,0,0,0,,That is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.38,Kingdom-Main,Changping,0,0,0,,Breaking through an army alone...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:53.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君）だが 実際に起こった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:53.71,Kingdom-Main,Changwenjun,0,0,0,,But it did indeed happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:59.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,龐煖は１人で全てを突破し\N迎え撃った摎の命を奪った
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:56.90,Kingdom-Main,Changwenjun,0,0,0,,Pang Nuan broke through everything on his own,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:59.64,Kingdom-Main,Changwenjun,0,0,0,,ambushed Liao, and killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:02.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…して その後 龐煖は？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:02.60,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,So what happened to Pang Nuan after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:11.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君）\N騒ぎに駆けつけた王騎に斬られた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:11.21,Kingdom-Main,Changwenjun,0,0,0,,He was cut down by Wang Qi, who had flew at him in a rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:15.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あそこまで\N激情に駆られた王騎を見たのは―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.58,0:18:17.76,Kingdom-Main,Changwenjun,0,0,0,,That was the first and last time I saw Wang Qi so swept into a passionate fury...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:18.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれが最初で最後だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:21.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（呂不韋）王騎が龐煖を斬った…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:21.44,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,Wang Qi cut down Pang Nuan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:24.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 死んだと思っていた龐煖は\N生きていて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:25.12,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,But Pang Nuan, whom was thought to be dead, is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:29.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かつ 今 その２人が両軍の将として\N相まみえようとしている
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:27.78,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,And now those two are likely to meet each other again
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:29.30,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,as leaders of the two opposing armies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:32.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少々できすぎだな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:31.80,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,This is a bit more than we expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:35.53,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,Most likely, Wang Qi knew about this from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:36.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君）恐らく\N王騎は初めから知っておったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:39.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 秦国軍総大将を引き受けた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:39.20,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,That is why he accepted to be the Supreme Commander of the State of Qin Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:44.94,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,This war is a battle that was deeply ingrained in the destinies of the two of them nine years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:45.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この戦いは\N９年前に深く刻まれた因縁の戦いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:49.69,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,Wang Qi is sure to have many comrades he lost in war... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.51,0:18:50.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）王騎には\N失った戦友は数多くいるだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:52.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ今回だけ動いた？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:52.08,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,but why has he only now moved? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:54.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,六将同士だからか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:54.34,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,Because they were fellow members of the Six Great Generals? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.85,0:19:00.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 王騎にとって\N摎は何か特別な存在だったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.89,0:18:59.93,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,No, perhaps Liao was someone special to Wang Qi...? {Thought. I'd make a gay joke if it wasn't obvious that Liao is female.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:04.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌平君）合点のいかぬ所がある
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:04.11,Kingdom-Main,Changping,0,0,0,,There is one point I do not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:08.26,Kingdom-Main,Changping,0,0,0,,You say that nine years ago, Pang Nuan attacked Liao's troops alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:08.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,９年前 龐煖は\N１人で摎の本陣を襲ったようだが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:10.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その意図は何だったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:10.17,Kingdom-Main,Changping,0,0,0,,but what was his goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:12.65,Kingdom-Main,Changping,0,0,0,,No matter how powerful Pang Nuan is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:12.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,龐煖の武力が いかほどであれ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:15.78,Kingdom-Main,Changping,0,0,0,,those actions seem considerably reckless for a Zhao Army strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.66,0:19:15.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,趙軍の作戦としては\N随分と乱暴だと思うが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:17.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君）あれは趙軍とは無関係だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:18.13,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,That had nothing to do with the Zhao Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:20.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（李斯）\Nなんだと？ どういう意味だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:20.00,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,What? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:22.68,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,Pang Nuan did not do that as a Zhao Army soldier,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:26.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君）龐煖は趙軍の兵ではなく\Nただ個人的な理由で摎を襲ったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:26.19,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,he attacked Liao for his own, personal reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:29.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌平君）私怨ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:28.80,Kingdom-Main,Changping,0,0,0,,A grudge?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:33.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君）それとも少し違う\N（昌平君）なぜ言い切れます？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:31.02,Kingdom-Main,Changwenjun,0,0,0,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:33.69,Kingdom-Main,Changping,0,0,0,,How can you say for sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:36.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツ本人の口から聞いたからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:36.60,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,Because I heard it from the man himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:44.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兵も軍も趙も秦も…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:44.07,Kingdom-Flashback,Pang,0,0,0,,Soldiers, armies, Zhao, Qin,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:47.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,取るに足らぬ ただの小事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:47.42,Kingdom-Flashback,Pang,0,0,0,,they are all inconsequential, mere trifles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:54.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるのは 天地さえ恐るる存在が\N今 この地に２人いるということ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.11,0:19:54.11,Kingdom-Flashback,Pang,0,0,0,,There are only two people on this land that make even heaven and earth tremble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:56.78,Kingdom-Flashback,Pang,0,0,0,,Me, and one other...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.74,0:19:57.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我のほかに もう１人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:20:02.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは\N天地が砕け散ろうとも 許せぬこと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:20:02.34,Kingdom-Flashback,Pang,0,0,0,,Even if it causes heaven and earth to be destroyed, I cannot allow that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:07.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）ウワーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.69,0:20:10.43,Kingdom-Flashback,Pang,0,0,0,,I am War God Pang Nuan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.75,0:20:10.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（龐煖）我 武神 龐煖なり！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:14.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出てこい 我が敵よ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.53,0:20:13.97,Kingdom-Flashback,Pang,0,0,0,,Show yourself, my enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:21.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？ それは　意味が分からぬ\Nその男 常軌を逸しておる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.06,0:20:19.25,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,What does that mean? I have no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:21.61,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,That man is completely insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:26.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに まともではなかった\Nだが それが龐煖という男なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:23.75,Kingdom-Main,Changwenjun,0,0,0,,It's true, he was abnormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.75,0:20:26.62,Kingdom-Main,Changwenjun,0,0,0,,But that's the kind of man Pang Nuan is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:30.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うむ… なるほど 面白そうな男だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:30.11,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,I see. He sounds like an interesting fellow.
