Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:53.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,十分 考えられます
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:54.02,Kingdom-Main,Changping,0,0,0,,I think it's well worth considering.
